76
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:44,750
<i>The farther from 0 you go, the greater 
the difference in the tangible world.</i>

77
00:06:46,020 --> 00:06:50,600
<i>You might have a different occupation tha
n you did in world 0, or a different spouse.</i>

78
00:06:51,670 --> 00:06:55,190
<i>Still, they're all worlds 
that your choices can lead to.</i>

79
00:06:56,890 --> 00:07:01,380
<i>The first time I made 
a major choice was when I was 7.</i>

80
