all go on outings together.</i>

88
00:07:26,690 --> 00:07:29,670
<i>But, once fun time was over,</i>

89
00:07:29,670 --> 00:07:34,430
<i>we'd leave my dad, and I'd go with 
my mom back to her childhood home.</i>

90
00:07:35,690 --> 00:07:38,150
